snippet.title: Jumpstart Baby Full Walkthrough (1998 Classic Version)
snippet.description:
Jumpstart Baby Full Walkthrough (1998 Classic Version)

Jumpstart Baby (1998 Classic Version) is a game created by Knowledge Adventure in 1998. It focuses on learning concepts for ages 9-24 months.
